      "id": "936f2f74-c4ed-28fa-5eae-c6dc0d25102d",
      "name": "Note: Read Source Feed"
    },
    {
      "parameters": {
        "content": "### Skip Already-Seen Posts\n\nCross-execution dedupe: remembers keys it has processed before and drops repeats — the idempotency guard.\n\nNext: Keep Top Stories",
        "width": 280,
        "height": 232,
        "color": 2
