      "id": "1529726f-3c89-e507-4861-89e7cf427719",
      "name": "Note: Skip Already-Seen Posts"
    },
    {
      "parameters": {
        "content": "### Keep Top Stories\n\nCaps the stream at 5 items to protect downstream quotas.\n\nNext: Rewrite for Our Audience (AI)",
