    },
    {
      "parameters": {
        "content": "### Rewrite for Our Audience (AI)\n\nSingle fixed LLM step (no tool choice) — cheaper and more predictable than an agent.\n\nPorts: ①→ Publish to Slack · ②→ Capture Failure Context\n\n⚠ failures exit via the error rail",
        "width": 280,
        "height": 232,
